<title>UK: BOE revises shortage to 1.25 bln stg, offers help.</title>
<headline>BOE revises shortage to 1.25 bln stg, offers help.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-04-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Bank of England invited UK money market operators to offer outright bills and repos to May 1 and 2 to help alleviate a revised forecast 1.25 billion stg liquidity shortage in the market.</p>
</text>
